<sect2 id='other-projects-of-interest'><title id='other-projects-of-interest-title'>Other Projects of Interest</title>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>[http://tor.eff.org/ Tor] - interesting onion-router network sponsored by EFF
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>[http://larytet.sourceforge.net/btRat.shtml Rodi] - Java program with encryption, content-search and optional IP spoofing
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>[http://anonet.fshell.org/ AnoNet: Cooperative Chaos] - a virtual IP network, uses OpenVPN and OSFP
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>[http://antsp2p.sourceforge.net/ ANts P2P] - Java program with encryption, IRC-based peer discovery, routing
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>[http://mute-net.sourceforge.net/ MUTE] - avoids direct connections
</para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</sect2>
